return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615561\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104raq1665702640601.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/raq1665702640601.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/raq1665702640601.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"raq1665702640601\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether the biggest label in tab set defines the tab size used for all tabs, or the tab size varies with its label.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"raq1665702640601__p_d103745e1_d103746e1_d103747e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>FixedWidth<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"raq1665702640601__table_d12233e1_d12234e1_d12235e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"raq1665702640601__table_d12233e1_d12234e1_d12235e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"raq1665702640601__table_d12233e1_d12234e1_d12235e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"raq1665702640601__table_d12233e1_d12234e1_d12235e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"raq1665702640601__table_d12233e1_d12234e1_d12235e1__entry__2\">All tabs have the same size, based on the tab with\n                     the longest label text.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"raq1665702640601__table_d12233e1_d12234e1_d12235e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"raq1665702640601__table_d12233e1_d12234e1_d12235e1__entry__2\">Each tab is sized according to its label\n                     text.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"raq1665702640601__section_n4z_ffn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1174617e111\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"raq1665702640601__table_d12236e1_d12237e1_d12238e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Ignored in any of the following cases:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"raq1665702640601__ul_yxq_hfn_wwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"raq1665702640601__li_d41636e1_d41637e1_d41638e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Width</span> has a value. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"raq1665702640601__li_d41639e1_d41640e1_d41641e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Justified</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"raq1665702640601__li_d41642e1_d41643e1_d41644e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Orientation</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">stack</code> or\n                                 <code class=\"ph codeph\">accordian</code>. In this case, the width of the tabs is\n                              the full width of the widget. </li>\n</ul></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"raq1665702640601__section_ftk_jfn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1174617e186\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"raq1665702640601__p_d103754e1_d103755e1_d103756e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see the \"$properties\" and \"$fieldproperties\" topics.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"raq1665702640601__pre_qtw_kfn_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"FixedWidth=false\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"raq1665702640601__section_mhb_lfn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1174617e204\">Example: Variable Tab Width</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"raq1665702640601__p_d103760e1_d103761e1_d103762e1\">If <code class=\"ph codeph\">FixedWidth</code> is set to false, the\n            size of tabs varies with the length of the label.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"raq1665702640601__fig_d103763e1_d103764e1_d103765e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Variable Tab Width</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"Variable tab width\" class=\"image\" id=\"raq1665702640601__image_cmv_nfn_wwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/tabwidth_variable.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"raq1665702640601__section_izq_4fn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1174617e229\">Example: Fixed Tab Width</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"raq1665702640601__p_d103772e1_d103773e1_d103774e1\">By default, <code class=\"ph codeph\">FixedWidth</code> is\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>, so the label size is fixed:</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"raq1665702640601__fig_d103775e1_d103776e1_d103777e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>Fixed Tab Size</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"Fixed tab size\" class=\"image\" id=\"raq1665702640601__image_sfc_tfn_wwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/tabwidth_fixed.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"raq1665702640601__section_lsx_tfn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1174617e256\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"raq1665702640601__ul_p3d_wfn_wwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"raq1665702640601__li_d41645e1_d41646e1_d41647e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bzj1665702641924.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzj1665702641924.html\" title=\"The utab widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tab, which is mapped to utab.\">utab (Tab)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"raq1665702640601__li_d41648e1_d41649e1_d41650e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lso1665702640824.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Tab Width (TabWidth)</a><p>Width of all tabs in the widget, in character cells. By default, the tab size is based on the length of the longest label,or the size of the default image. Value is a number; minimum is 5 characters.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nym1665702640684.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Justified (Justify)</a><p>Justifies the tabs so that they occupy the full width of the tab widget. Default is False.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fqh1665702641252.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Tab Orientation ( TabOrientation)</a><p>Orientation of the tab strip. The default is Horizontal.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$properties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldproperties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615561\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615561\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Fixed Tab Width (FixedWidth) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Determines whether the biggest label in tab set defines the tab size used for all tabs, or the tab size varies with its label. \" FixedWidth = True | False \" Value Description True All tabs have the same size, based on the tab with the longest label text. False Each tab is sized according to its label text. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Ignored in any of the following cases: Tab Width has a value. Justified is True Tab Orientation is stack or accordian . In this case, the width of the tabs is the full width of the widget. Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see the \"$properties\" and \"$fieldproperties\" topics. $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"FixedWidth=false\" Copy Example: Variable Tab Width If FixedWidth is set to false, the size of tabs varies with the length of the label. Figure 1. Variable Tab Width Example: Fixed Tab Width By default, FixedWidth is true , so the label size is fixed: Figure 2. Fixed Tab Size Applies to utab (Tab) utabex (TabEx) Related Links Tab Width (TabWidth) Width of all tabs in the widget, in character cells. By default, the tab size is based on the length of the longest label,or the size of the default image. Value is a number; minimum is 5 characters. Justified (Justify) Justifies the tabs so that they occupy the full width of the tab widget. Default is False. Tab Orientation ( TabOrientation) Orientation of the tab strip. The default is Horizontal. $properties Return or set the current widget properties of a field. $fieldproperties Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}